<h4>Welcome to Quickroute!</h4>
<p>This is a bare-bones application for demonstration. Create a user with /bin/create_user.pl to test the form below.</p>
<p>Check out /templates and /routes.pl to see how this sample site is set up.</p>
<form method='POST'>
  <p>username: <input type = 'text' name = 'username' /></p>
  <p>password: <input type = 'password' name = 'password' /></p>
  <p>remember me? <input type = 'checkbox' name = 'remember' unchecked /></p>
  <button type='submit'>Log In</button>
</form>

